LEGENDS
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-----------------------------------------------------------
Pattern 7 
-----------------------------------------------------------
* * * * * * *
* *       * *
*   *   *   *
*     *     *
*   *   *   *
* *       * *
* * * * * * *
-----------------------------------------------------------
Pattern 8
-----------------------------------------------------------

* * * * * * * * *
* *     *     * *
*   *   *   *   *
*     * * *     *
* * * * * * * * *
*     * * *     *
*   *   *   *   *
* *     *     * *
* * * * * * * * *

------------------------------------------------------------
with the help of above pattern an alphabet can be printed
------------------------------------------------------------
				c=0    c=n/2    c=n-1

	r=0			* * * * * * * * *
				* *     *     * *
				*   *   *   *   *	r + c = n -1
				*     * * *     *
	r=n/2		* * * * * * * * *
				*     * * *     *
				*   *   *   *   *	r == c
				* *     *     * *
	r=n-1		* * * * * * * * *